properties.Description: Metadata describing a graph query for an Azure resource.

etag.Description: This will be used to handle Optimistic Concurrency. If not present, it will always overwrite the existing resource without checking conflict.

timeModified.Description: Date and time in UTC of the last modification that was made to this graph query definition.

description.Description: The description of a graph query.

query.Description: KQL query that will be graph.

resultKind.Description: Enum indicating a type of graph query.
